### List users as admin
GET http://localhost:8080/users
X-User-Id: admin

### List users as standard user (read-only allowed)
GET http://localhost:8080/users
X-User-Id: alice

### Get single user
GET http://localhost:8080/users/bob
X-User-Id: alice

### Create user as admin
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: admin

{
  "id": "charlie",
  "name": "Charlie",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Update user as admin
PUT http://localhost:8080/users/bob
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: admin

{
  "name": "Bobby",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Forbidden update as standard user
PUT http://localhost:8080/users/bob
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: alice

{
  "name": "Malicious",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}
